data.title: S: Discography of New Age, Electronic, and Ambient Music
data.meta_description:
Discography of New Age, Electronic, and Ambient
			    Music.  Compiled by Piero Scaruffi.  A list of
			    albums by over 600 new age and electronic music
			    artists.  Lists of music labels and magazines.
			    Last updated December 1997.
			    HTML by Harvey Chinn (harvey.chinn@juno.com).
